title: Dior Saddle Messenger Bag
description: Dior Saddle messenger bag in black grainy calfskin leather (year 2019). Featuring silver-toned hardware, a zipper pocket with mini saddle flap. The main magnetic saddle flap opens to a main compartment lined with black textile. Approximate dimensions: 24cm(W) x 14cm(H) x 3cm(D), body wrist length: 37-52cm, adjustable. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
